sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>configurable/TCP HTTP/2
    participant Handler as HTTP REST API Handler
    participant MM as ModelManager
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph Engine
    participant LLMCalc as LLM Calculator
    participant OVRuntime as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant OVGenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>ContinuousBatchingPipeline
    participant FSFactory as FileSystem Factory
    participant S3 as Amazon S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant GCS as Google Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: REST Model Inference (KServe v2)
    Client->>KRBAC: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward (HTTP plaintext)<br/>AuthN/AuthZ verified
    REST->>Handler: Route request
    Handler->>MM: GetModel + Infer
    MM->>OVRuntime: Execute inference<br/>(C++ API, in-process)
    OVRuntime-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>Handler: Response tensor
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>KRBAC: HTTP response
    KRBAC-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: LLM Chat Completions (Streaming SSE)
    Client->>KRBAC: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    KRBAC->>REST: Forward (HTTP plaintext)
    REST->>Handler: Route to generative handler
    Handler->>Handler: Validate Bearer Token<br/>(--api_key_file)
    Handler->>MP: Execute LLM graph
    MP->>LLMCalc: Process chat request
    LLMCalc->>OVGenAI: ContinuousBatchingPipeline<br/>(speculative decoding, prefix caching)
    loop Token-by-token generation
        OVGenAI-->>LLMCalc: Next token
        LLMCalc-->>REST: SSE chunk<br/>(text/event-stream)
        REST-->>KRBAC: SSE chunk
        KRBAC-->>Client: SSE chunk (HTTPS)
    end
    LLMCalc-->>REST: [DONE] event
    REST-->>Client: Stream complete

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Model Loading from Cloud Storage
    MM->>FSFactory: Resolve storage backend<br/>(s3:// / gs:// / az://)
    alt S3 Storage
        FSFactory->>S3: HTTPS GET<br/>TLS 1.2+, AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>FSFactory: Model artifacts
    else GCS Storage
        FSFactory->>GCS: HTTPS GET<br/>TLS 1.2+, OAuth 2.0
        GCS-->>FSFactory: Model artifacts
    end
    FSFactory-->>MM: Model files (local temp)
    MM->>OVRuntime: loadModel (in-process)

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: HuggingFace Model Pull
    MM->>HFHub: git clone via libgit2<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
    HFHub-->>MM: Repository + LFS files
    MM->>OVRuntime: loadModel (in-process)
